txt.en: Naethír can be found in the central Fields of Fornost, north of the road leading west towards Evendim.\n\nYou should defeat Naethír, for this being has sapped the warmth from the Fields of Fornost.

You feel a terrible chill, and realize that a great and old evil presence is near.\n\nYou have encounted Naethír, a terrifying presence in the Fields of Fornost. This ghostly being has gained power from having pulled the life from the lands around it.
